tps://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-brushes-her-teeth-with-a-bottle-of-jack-to-mark-tik-tok-reaching-one-billion-spotify-streams-3782230">凯莎用一瓶杰克刷牙以纪念《TiK ToK》突破 10 亿 Spotify 流媒体的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
